{"build_type":"library","description":"Reusable in-RAM dependency-graph collector: given a roots array (document-sequence of directory-path strings), enumerate the package universe under those roots (enumerate_universe_packages, which validates/filters: skips dotfiles, unparseable files, packages with no package_name) and build the dependency graph as a document-sequence of per-package entry records. Returned in memory so both the build-package-dependency-relation-graph executable (emits it to stdout) and cross-reference-symbol-across-dependency-graph (consumes it directly) share one builder. Reuses enumerate_universe_packages, begin_empty_sequence_document_value, count_members_inside_container_value, append_graph_entry_per_universe_package.","module_name":"collect-dependency-graph-starting-roots-sequence","package_name":"collect-dependency-graph-starting-roots-sequence","function_definitions":{"collect-dependency-graph-starting-roots-sequence":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"roots_array","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"enumerate-every-declared-universe-package","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"roots_array"}],"result_assignment_variable":"universe","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"begin-empty-sequence-document-value","invocation_arguments":[],"result_assignment_variable":"graph","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"count-members-inside-container-value","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"universe"}],"result_assignment_variable":"n","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"append-graph-entry-across-universe-package","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":